sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as trainer-controller-manager
    participant JobSetCtrl as JobSet Controller
    participant TrainingPod as Training Pod<br/>2113/TCP HTTP
    participant LauncherPod as MPI Launcher Pod
    participant NodePods as MPI Node Pods<br/>2222/TCP SSH

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,JobSetCtrl: Flow 1: TrainJob Reconciliation
        User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply TrainJob<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OIDC/SA)
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-trainer-...-trainjob<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS, TLS, API server cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (allow/deny)
        K8sAPI-->>User: TrainJob created

        Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch TrainJob<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: TrainJob event

        Note over Controller: Resolve TrainingRuntime/<br/>ClusterTrainingRuntime,<br/>enforce ML policy via plugins

        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create JobSet CR<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy (RHAI)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
        JobSetCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch JobSet<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>JobSetCtrl: JobSet event
        JobSetCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Jobs/Pods<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Controller,TrainingPod: Flow 2: RHAI Progression Tracking
        Controller->>K8sAPI: List pods (API reader)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pod list with IPs
        Controller->>TrainingPod: GET /metrics<br/>2113/TCP HTTP, No encryption<br/>Auth: NetworkPolicy (source IP)
        TrainingPod-->>Controller: Training progress metrics
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Update TrainJob status<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    end

    rect rgb(245, 230, 255)
        Note over Controller,NodePods: Flow 3: MPI Training Setup
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create SSH Secret (ECDSA)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Hostfile ConfigMap<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
        Note over LauncherPod,NodePods: After pods scheduled
        LauncherPod->>NodePods: SSH connection<br/>2222/TCP SSH (ECDSA)<br/>Public key auth
        NodePods-->>LauncherPod: Training coordination
    end
